  "title": "Her Win on the Table Beside Yours, Both Real",
  "subtitle": "A visualisation for seeing another woman's success alongside your own without one diminishing the other",
  "excerpt": "A short visualisation for the moment when comparison is running. Two things on the same table: her win and yours. Neither larger, neither in competition with the other. Both real.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Written for homemade.education.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A short visualisation for placing two things beside each other without one cancelling the other out. Her win. Yours. The practice is about proximity without competition.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to visualisation? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how visualisation works",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/how-visualisation-works"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Sit quietly. Close your eyes or soften your gaze.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Picture a large, clean table, plain surface, no clutter. Place her win on the table as an object. Don't make it small, don't make it large. Just an object. Real.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Now place yours on the table beside it. The thing you want most in your own money situation, the version of success that belongs to you. Real, too.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Look at both objects. They don't touch. They don't compete for space. The table is big enough for both.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Stay with this for two minutes. Neither object has to move. Neither shrinks because the other is there.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Written for homemade.education.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
